Create Approved Cases, YoY, by Job Categories 14

Creating Approved Cases by Job Categories

-          Click on Clustered column, Then drag and drop Job Categories on Shared Axis

-          Drag and drop Approved Cases on Column Value, Drag and drop YoY on Line Value

-          Click on Format- then General.  Y =367, Width = 554, Height = 349

-          Click on X -On- Color -Black, Text size 9, Title -Off

-          Click on Y-On-Color-Black-Text 9- start 0.01, Gridline-On, Color-Grey- Stroke -1 Secondary -On, Color Black, Title -Off

-          Click Data label -On, Color Black, Customize-On, Approved Cases-Show-On, Color White

-          Data color- On-  YOY= Color -Sky Blue-#118dFF- Brown-#a38600

-          Shapes-On, Shade area-On, Stoke 3,Show Marker-On. Size 5 Marker color Sky blue #118dFF

-          Title- On, Text Approved Cases by YoY and Job categories- Font White, Word wrap-On,

-          Background Color Brown-#6d5a00- Align- Center- Text size-14

-          Click Background on- Color light grey
